message.body: Gabi! Do you have a wee bit of time Monday? Kelsey and I are coming into Burlington for the day and I would love to see your face!
Omg we shall see! I'll see if Kelsey wants to stay, she doesn't work till noon Tuesday.
Just monday!?! Mondays really tight, i work til 3, walk simone, go to teach at guitar center, then spielpalast has a fundraiser monday night. You should stick around for monday night
